We can accept check or credit card donations in person or via U.S. Mail. To donate by mail, please print and fill out the following form and mail it to: 

Yanick Fourcand
Mission Personnel
The Episcopal Church Center
815 Second Ave.
New York, NY 10017

Click here or use the attachment to this email to download and print the form. 

In order to make sure a check gets to us and is also tax-deductible as a charitable contribution, please make checks out to âThe Episcopal Churchâ or âDFMSâ (Domestic and Foreign Missionary Society) and put our names in the memo line. 

At this time, we are unfortunately unable to accept credit card donations directly over the internet. We are working hard toward implementing a solution that will make such direct donations possible and secure. For the time being, you can donate by credit card by providing your information on the donation form. 

If you have any questions, or if you prefer to donate in person, please contact us at blocher@gmail.com.



